import pandas as pd
import math

def process_s(s):
    results = []
    results.append(s.iloc[1])
    results.append(s.iloc[:3].tolist())
    results.append(s[s > s.median()].tolist())
    results.append(s.iloc[[4, 3, 1]].tolist())
    results.append([math.exp(val) for val in s])
    return results
